
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "SearchesMenu";
}

<img class="img_small" src="~/Content/travel.png" data-toggle="toggle" data-target="#demo">

<div class ="slider" id="demo">
    <h4 id="titleText">Travel Search</h4>
    <p>
        By providing your full address, or that of a college your interested in, you can learn the travel ratings of the area.
        This information is provided though 
        <a href="https://www.walkscore.com/professional/"> Walk Score </a>
        and will tell you the ratings (0-100) of the areas walkability, biking and local transit. This will help prospective
        college students learn what their tranportation options are for cities of interest.
    </p>
    <button type="button" id="searchButton" class="btn btn-info" onclick="@("window.location.href='" + @Url.Action("Travel", "Home") + "'");">Try It!</button>
</div>

<img class="img_small" src="~/Content/food.png" data-toggle="toggle" data-target="#demo2">

<div class="slider" id="demo2">
    <h4 id="titleText">Food Search</h4>
    <p>
        By utilizing
        <a href="https://www.yelp.com/"> Yelp! </a>
        we provide you a comprehensive search of any city of interest, be it a random whim or a
        college city of interest, to find food option in that area. You can either run a search for Grocery options or a search for
        Delivery in the area - allowing students to find food that accomidates their lifestyle needs. Results include a link to the
        locations so you can further investigate them on your own.
    </p>
    <button type="button" id="searchButton" class="btn btn-info" onclick="@("window.location.href='" + @Url.Action("Yelp", "Home") + "'");">Try It!</button>
</div>

<img class="img_small" src="~/Content/people.png" data-toggle="toggle" data-target="#demo3">

<div class="slider" id="demo3">
    <h4 id="titleText">People Search</h4>
    <p>
        A major component to any new lifestyle is finding people you can enjoy it with. This search, which uses census data gathered by
        <a href="https://market.mashape.com/mapfruition/demographicinquiry/overview"> Demographic Inquiry, </a>
        to tell you all about who lives in the city of interest. From this search you can learn about what types of people, by age,
        race and gender. This, we hope, will enable you to find you friends and a good community to start your new college life right!
    </p>
    <button type="button" id="searchButton" class="btn btn-info" onclick="@("window.location.href='" + @Url.Action("Demographic", "Home") + "'");">Try It!</button>
</div>